classitems.description:
Text to be applied to the ordering buttons of the ordering list.  The text should be arranged as an object in
JSON notation.

eg. {first: ..., up: ..., down: ..., last: ...}

Text to be applied to the ordering buttons of the target list.  The text should be arranged as an object in
